@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yowwey(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    tmp = (v0 / wp.exp((tmp + 0.42 - tmp + 0.14)))
    v0 = wp.abs(tmp)
    tmp = (wp.cos(tmp) + ((v2 + 0.44 / v1 + 0.87) * 0.74))
    v1 = wp.exp(0.38)
    v2 = ((0.46 * wp.abs(v1 + 0.60)) - ((v1 + 0.18 * v2 + 0.99) - 0.95))
    v2 = wp.cos(0.42)
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
